title: 02/16/2021 – The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: 02/16/2021 – The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
With Rob Parker and TJ Houshmandzadeh filling in for Dan Patrick and the Danettes, the guys try to make sense of the future of Carson Wentz with either Chicago or Indianapolis as teams look to acquire the embattled Eagles QB, Urban Meyer has his “welcome to the NFL” moment and the guys think he misread the room, and former NFL head coach Hue Jackson joins the show.
